{
  "stem": "13623.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In dribs and drabs, we're starting to hear that the war is going bad for Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We heard rumors, but we-- this time we heard it from prisoners that were evacuated from Auschwitz because the Russian front got close to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Germany, the-- the SS did not want any of the prisoners to be liberated by the Allies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we heard little rumors here and there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that work detail, these prisoners blended in with the rest of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest-- the rest of the camp went about going to work every day and standing appell in the morning and at night.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Things were going as-- as routinely as possible at the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Camp life went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How were you working underground?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For-- for the B-1 missiles?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not too long because after having these-- all these various jobs, it wasn't too long before Dora was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say in February of '45.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're all standing, what they called Zahlappell, where everybody's standing out and we're being counted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We're all given, each one of us, in the past we each got a loaf of bread the size of a brick for three people, each one of us is given a loaf of bread per person.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're being told we're being-- we're going to another camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This piece of bread is enough for three days for you, and after that, you'll be fed again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people, being that we were so hungry, finished that-- that loaf of bread within an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some people tried to ration the bread and listen to what they told us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That it will have to last us for three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried to ration it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
